1) source: https://www.allabtai.com/how-to-master-reverse-prompt-engineering-with-chatgpt/
2) date: FEBRUARY 13, 2023
3) The article on "How to Master Reverse Prompt Engineering with ChatGPT" is a comprehensive guide that explains how to use reverse prompt engineering to fine-tune GPT-3 language models. 
And covers the concept of prompts, and how reverse prompt engineering involves working backwards from the desired output to create a suitable prompt for a language model.
The step-by-step process for using reverse prompt engineering, along with tips and best practices, are discussed in detail. 
Also highlights potential applications, including generating content for social media or e-commerce platforms, and improving the accuracy of search engine results.
